def hide():
    print_slow("You run towards a bunch of crates, moving as quickly and quietly as you can, you climb into one of the crates ")
    print_slow("and slow your breathing as best as you can. You start hearing footsteps get closer and louder,")
    print_slow("“STOMP…”")
    print_slow("“STOMP…”")
    print_slow("“STOMP…”")
    print_slow("And then silence.")
    print_slow("The stench of terror stopped just as quickly as it started, but this time leaving a misty aura in the air which seemed")
    print_slow(" to be entering the crate the you are inside. Making you cough lightly but getting louder and louder.. ")
    print_slow("Lucy’s footsteps are still no where to be heard.")
    print_slow("Unbeknownst to you; Lucy can detect the scent of your blood from within the confines of hers pace, a revelation that ")
    print_slow("unfolds to you as she playfully manipulates every part of her surrounding. She swipes hard into the crate ")
    print_slow("with her right arm, making the crate fly across the room and making you fall out from it, injuring his leg.")
    print_slow(" Before you have a chance to react Lucy is already on top of you, tearing your legs from your body ")
    print_slow("one by one with each scream reaching a higher pitch than the one before it. ")
    print_slow("Inflicting an agonizing and slow demise upon you, Lucy relishes her blood-infused feast while scientists ")
    print_slow("proudly observe the blood-filled violence from behind a protective window. A bizarre paternal tenderness lingers")
    print_slow(" in the air as they proudly oversee the fruits of their labour from their in-house experiment, eyes never escaping ")
    print_slow("not even for a second from each thrash and chomp coming from Lucy into your blood savoured body. You look ")
    print_slow("beside your blood severed body whilst you feel huge chunks being ripped out from you and notice a bright torch")
    print_slow(" left on the corner of a cell, this cell even has a tiny window attached to it, looking out towards ")
    print_slow("the woods…this must have been Lucy’s room. You can feel the blood squirting out of your body in vast ")
    print_slow("out of consciousness and vividly hear voices and loud banging coming from the other side of the door you")
    print_slow(" was attempting to unlock. You also hear name being screamed from behind the door,")
    print_slow(" it must be Lucas, Michelle and Toby, ")
    print_slow("the rest of your search party.. But they are too late…")
    print_slow2("                                             ..                                                    ")
    print_slow2("                                        :!JPB##&&&&&&##BPJ!:                                        ")  
