def stay_hidden():
    print_slow("You decide to stay hidden and this time look for a key, you find one, pick it up. Now you have three options inside this room, they are to:")
    print_slow("1. Unlock Lucy's cage.")
    print_slow("2. Free Hostages.")
    print_slow("3. Run for the white light door.")
 
    new_choice = input("Please choose option (1, 2, or 3): ")
 
    if new_choice == "1":
        unlock_cage()
    elif new_choice == "2":
        free_hostages()
    elif new_choice == "3":
        run_to_heaven()
    else:
        print_slow("Invalid choice, please choose 1, 2, or 3")
 
 
def free_hostages():
    print_slow("You attempt to take the key from a guard. He notices you and turns around before you have any time to react and hits you over the head, making you black out. Slowly opening your eyes, you come to the realization that you are unable to move, you look down and notice your hands are bound to the table on either side, you feel weak and drowsy. As you raise your eyes higher, you notice a mirror facing you. You then hear:“Scientist: Excellent, this is the perfect specimen, the calcium in his bone structure is even stronger than Lucy's.. “Your eyes travel around the mirror as they open wider and you finally notice that your cranium has been cut off and is resting beside you on a metal table and scientists are dissecting your brain, with pieces already thrown across the floor. You let out a terrifying scream, even making the scientists feel the bone-curdling terror come from your mouth… “Scientist 1: QUICK! SEDATE HIM!” One of the scientists reach for a syringe filled with a black liquid with shaky hands, unlike anything in existence and injects this substance into your body, green goo oozes out from your belly button and just as this happens you start to fall back unconscious… to be continued.")
